 113:Src/clock.c   ****     /*
 114:Src/clock.c   ****      * Enable one-pulse mode (OPM):
 115:Src/clock.c   ****      *   CR1 bit 3: OPM — One-pulse mode
 116:Src/clock.c   ****      *   0: Counter is not stopped at update event
 117:Src/clock.c   ****      *   1: Counter stops counting at the next update event (clearing CEN)
 118:Src/clock.c   ****      *
 119:Src/clock.c   ****      * With OPM, the timer counts from 0 to ARR, sets UIF, then stops
 120:Src/clock.c   ****      * automatically. We do not need to manually clear CEN after a delay.
